zhenwu_sun.002 = { #孫重進 Sun Chongjin or 李存進 Li Cunjin. Son of Sun Quan. (後唐招討使李存進墓碑) In 893.5.20 given name 李存進. (後唐招討使李存進墓碑) In 900 made 永安軍使, 北都知兵馬使. (舊五代史/卷53) In 900.5.31 made 知汾州軍州. (後唐招討使李存進墓碑) 906.3.28 made 知石州軍州事. (後唐招討使李存進墓碑) In 908.2.5 made 石州刺史. (後唐招討使李存進墓碑) In 912.1.22 made 知汾州軍州事. (後唐招討使李存進墓碑) In 914.3.30 made 慈州刺史. (後唐招討使李存進墓碑) 慈州刺史 until 914.12.20, on that day made 沁州刺史. (後唐招討使李存進墓碑) 沁州刺史 until 915.7.15, on that day made 天雄都巡按使. (資治通鑑/卷269) In 919.4.4 made 振武節度使. (後唐招討使李存進墓碑) 振武節度使 until 922.9.24, on that day killed in battle. (舊五代史/卷29)

zhenwu_sun.003 = { #孫漢韶 Sun Hanshao. Eldest son of Li Cunjin. (後唐招討使李存進墓碑) In 925.12.19 era made 蔡州刺史. (孫漢韶墓誌) In 926 changed surname back to 孫. (舊五代史/卷53) In 927.8.30 once again made 蔡州刺史. (孫漢韶墓誌) In 928.3.25 made 彰國軍節度觀風留後. (孫漢韶墓誌) 彰國軍節度觀風留後 until 929.5.12, on that day his mother died. (孫漢韶墓誌) In 932.2.17 made honorary 利州節度使. (舊五代史/卷43 and 孫漢韶墓誌) In 933.7.18 made 洋州節度使. (舊五代史/卷44) In 934.8.31 made 永平軍節度使. (資治通鑑/卷279) In 938.2.2 made 昭武軍節度使. (孫漢韶墓誌) In 939.7.19 made 山南節度使. (孫漢韶墓誌) In 944.6.23 once again made 山南節度使. (孫漢韶墓誌) In 947.7.21 made 武信節度使. (孫漢韶墓誌) In 954.4.6 once again made 武信節度使. (孫漢韶墓誌) 武信節度使 until 955.8.30, on that day died. (孫漢韶墓誌)

After the enthronment of Shengzong and regency of Queen dowager, Derang was relaged to palace guards. In 985 政事令. Next year lead forces in victory over Cao Bin and Mi Xin, for which was made Duke of Chu and soon after elevated to Prince of Chu. In 994 北府宰相兼領樞密使 and soon after also 北院樞密使, elevated to rank 大丞相 and made Prince of Qi. At that time held power over whole Liao army. In 1011.4.11 died. (遼史/卷15)

1401693 = { #韓德威 Han Dewei, courtesy name 普鄰 Pulin. Fifth son of Han Kuangsi according to 惕隱司秦王帳空寧敵烈太保墓誌, third son according to 遼史. Between 969 and 979 made an official in Shangjing and prefect of Ruzhou 儒州防禦使, 北院宣徽使. In 983 because his father died, succeeded temporarily 西南招討使. Later this year five tribes of Tanguts raided southwest, Han Dewei Pacified them. Was made 領知突呂不部、迭剌部糾軍, pacified 稍古葛, and was made officially 西南招討使. In 986 together with Tigin Yelü Shanpu defeated Yang Ye. In 988 made 開府儀同三司, 政事令、門下平章事. Because Chengyi in Shanxi fell his command over troops was removed. In 992 Li Jiqian appeased Song, so Han Dewei led an expedition against Xi Xia and plundered Lingzhou. In 996 once again struck at Tanguts. Died the same year at the age of 55.
	dynasty = 1000048327 #Han
	name = "Dewei_name"
	religion = shangqing
	culture = han
	father = 1401679
	trait = education_martial_3
	942.1.1 = {
		birth = yes

1401741 = { #耶律恕 Yelü Ru, Khitan name 耨里 Nouli. Member of Han household according to 金史. Due to lack of futher data on the parenthood, I'll make him a son of Abu. He liked reading books. Due to his knowledge of both Khitan scripts was early given a post. In 1122 Tianzuo escaped west and Liao fell. In 3rd month Ru surrendered to Jin along with Yelü Gaoba and was made a general under the command of Wanyan Loushi. Together with Marshal Wanyan Zonghan they invaded Song, Ru led the vanguard. In 1133 he took part in the battle of Hesheng Plain under the command of Wanyan Zongbi. Next year he took part in the battle of Xianran pass. Due to his skillful command of troops he was recommended to the post of the deputy prefect of Taiyuan and Zhending by Wanyan Zongpu. Later made 行台兵部侍郎、尚書左司郎中. After the enthronment of Wanyan Liang he was made a 沁南軍節度使 and 工部尚書. In 1150 安國軍節度使. In 1153 參知政事. In 1154 prefect of Xingzhong. In 1156 retired and made a prince of Guangping. The same year he died.

1404804 = {#任得敬 Ren Dejing. First a Controller-general 通判 at Xi'an 西安州. In 1137 he surrendered to Xi Xia after Xi'an was taken by them. Made a prefect by Quanshun. In 1138 in order to curry a favour with the Emperor he introduced his daughter to the palace. In 1137 she became a concubine and he was made a Defense and Security Commissioner at Jingzhou 靜州防禦使. Due to bribery he rose in ranks at the court and became a high offical. In 1138 he was able to make his daughter an Empress, while he himself because Imperial father-in-law 上國丈爷 and he a Supreme Commander at Jingzhou 都統軍. In 1139 his daughter becomes Empress Dowager, even though the next Emperor is not her biological son. In 1140 as a reward for pacifying the rebellion of Xiao Heda 蕭合達 he is enfeoffed as Duke of Xiping 西平公 and made Supreme Commander of Xiangqing Army 翔慶軍都統軍. In 1143 he pacifies agrarian revolts in Xianzhou and Dingzhou 威州、定州等. In 1147 he conspires to have more say in the government, but is stopped by Wo Daozhong 斡道冲 and other ministers. In 1149 he is made 尚書令 中書令. In 1156 he becomes a Prime Minister 國相 after the death of Chage, his younger brothers Decong a Captain of Palace guards 殿前太尉, Degong Governor of Capital Prefecture Xingqing 興慶府尹. Soon after he forces Renzong to make him Prince of Chu 楚王. In 1165 he build a fortress in Lingzhou and a palace for himself, requests control over Shazhou, Guazhou, Lingzhou and Xiazhou. In 1170 he creates a fief for himself, Renzong is forced to consent and gives Southwestern Circuit 西南路, Xiping 西平府, Lingzhou 靈州 and other provinces to Chu. He asks for recognition from Jin, but is rebuked and instead offers a two-side attack on Jin to Song. However, his plot is discovered and Renzong with the support of Jin captures and executes Ren brothers in 8th month.

1800294 = { #封言道 Feng Yandao. In 640 made 駙馬都尉. In 641 married 淮南公主. In 642 made 汝州刺史. In 644 made 汴州刺史. In 653 made 寧州刺史. In 655 made 齊州刺史. In 656 made 蘄州刺史. In 663 made 金州刺史. In 665 made 虔州刺史. In 667 made 廣州刺史. In 675 made 滄州刺史. In 677 made 瀛洲刺史, soon after moved to 青州刺史. The same year made 檢校揚州大都督府長史. In 681 made 行并州大都督府長史. in 683 made 懷州刺史. In 684 made 汴州刺史. In 685 demoted to 貴州刺史. Soon after moved to 溫州刺史. Later to 滁州刺史. In 689 made 淄州刺史. In 690 made 普州刺史. In 692 made 婺州刺史. In 694 made 宋州刺史. (周故宋州刺史駙馬都尉上柱國蓨縣開國子封公墓志銘)

1800731 = { #富弼 Fu Bi. In 1030 made 知河南府長水縣. (富鄭公弼顯忠尚德之碑) Later made 河陽節度判官事, but demoted to 知睦州. (富鄭公弼顯忠尚德之碑) 通判絳州 until 1037, in that year made 太子中允，直集賢院. (富鄭公弼顯忠尚德之碑) 樞密副使 until 1044.8.30, on that day made 河北宣撫使. (宋史/卷211) 通判濮州 in 1044.11.17. (續資治通鑑長編/卷152) 江東轉運按察使 in 1045.8.31. (續資治通鑑長編/卷157) In 1045.2.7 made 京東西路安撫使兼知鄆州. (續資治通鑑長編/卷157) 知鄆州 in 1045.11.20. (續資治通鑑長編/卷157) 知鄆州 until 1047.6.24, on that day made 京東路安撫使知青州. (續資治通鑑長編/卷160) 知青州 until 1048.5.3, on that day made 禮部侍郎. (續資治通鑑長編/卷163) Next year made 知鄭州, later moved to 蔡州, 知河陽, 判并州兼河東經略安撫使. (富鄭公弼顯忠尚德之碑) After Wang Ze's rebellion (1048) made 知鄭、蔡、河陽, 判幷州. (宋史/卷313) 知河陽 in 1053.8.1. (續資治通鑑長編/卷175) 知河陽 until 1055.3.17, on that day made 宣徽南院使判并州. (續資治通鑑長編/卷178) 宣徽南院使、檢校太保、判幷州 until 1055.7.8, on that day made 同中書門下平章事. (宋史/卷211 and 續資治通鑑長編/卷179) In 1063.6.16 made 樞密使、檢校太師、行禮部尚書、同平章事. (宋史/卷211) In 1065.8.9 made 鎮海軍節度使, 判揚州. (宋史/卷313 and 宋史紀事本末/卷34) In 1065.8.9 made 鎮海軍節度使判河陽 [this is an error for 揚州]. (宋史/卷211) On Shenzong's enthronment (1068) made 武寜軍節度, soon after once again 判河陽. (富鄭公弼顯忠尚德之碑) In 1068 made 判汝州. (宋史/卷313 and 富鄭公弼顯忠尚德之碑) In 1069.2.24 made 左僕射、門下侍郎同平章事. (宋史/卷313) In 1069.8.20 made 判河南. (富鄭公弼顯忠尚德之碑) 左僕射兼門下侍郎、同平章事加檢校太師 until 1069.11.13, on that day made 武寧軍節度使判亳州. (宋史/卷211). 知亳州 in 1071.5.14. (續資治通鑑長編/卷222) Soon after once again made 判河陽.
